  "description": "Juicy roasted portobello mushrooms are the star of this plant-based dish. Serve with garlic cannellini mash (extra protein!) and a lamb's lettuce salad sprinkled with pumpkin seeds. Drizzle on a zingy homemade chimichurri made with fresh coriander and a chilli kick! (Gluten and dairy-free, suitable for coeliacs.)",
